00:37:58,378 --> 00:38:00,437
Did we get the girl out?

414
00:38:04,473 --> 00:38:06,420
Yes.

415
00:38:06,420 --> 00:38:08,120
That's good then.

416
00:38:08,612 --> 00:38:10,412
That's good.

