You didn't submit the application.

419
00:38:23,403 --> 00:38:25,207
It's all my fault.

420
00:38:34,599 --> 00:38:36,820
How is this your fault?

421
00:38:38,320 --> 00:38:40,539
It was my own decision.

422
00:38:42,890 --> 00:38:44,690
I was thinking

423
00:38:45,600 --> 00:38:47,880
I could stay with you for another year.

424
00:38:49,553 --> 00:38:51,752
But now it looks like...

425
00:38:52,800 --> 00:38:54,916
I have no other choice.

426
00:38:57,869 --> 00:38:59,606
It's all my fault.

427
00:38:59,606 --> 00:39:01,806
I shouldn't have gone to the meeting.

428
00:39:01,806 --> 00:39:04,609
I should have gone on the mission myself. I shouldn't have let you go.

429
00:39:04,609 --> 00:39:06,873
And this wouldn't have happened to you.

430
00:39:06,873 --> 00:39:08,373
It's all my fault.

431
00:39:11,516 --> 00:39:13,093
Song Yan.

432
00:39:13,093 --> 00:39:16,550
Song Yan, it has nothing to do with you.

433
00:39:17,299 --> 00:39:19,459
It was my own decision.

434
00:39:25,032 --> 00:39:26,572
Actually...

435
00:39:27,331 --> 00:39:29,770
I had a selfish reason.

436
00:39:29,770 --> 00:39:34,326
I was thinking that when I had children,

437
00:39:35,115 --> 00:39:37,989
I could tell them proudly

438
00:39:39,360 --> 00:39:42,480
