443
00:41:07,525 --> 00:41:10,486
Forward march!

444
00:41:20,460 --> 00:41:22,705
Halt!

445
00:41:22,705 --> 00:41:25,045
Mark!

446
00:41:27,054 --> 00:41:28,854
Halt!

447
00:41:36,804 --> 00:41:38,932
I hereby announce

448
00:41:38,932 --> 00:41:43,334
that Suo Jun, the instructor of Shili Tai Fire and Rescue Station,

449
00:41:43,334 --> 00:41:49,376
will proudly retire from the national comprehensive fire and rescue team

450
00:41:49,376 --> 00:41:52,746
and transfer to the local housing and construction department.

451
00:41:52,746 --> 00:41:57,915
Thank you for your eight years of dedication to the construction of our fire brigade,

452
00:41:57,915 --> 00:42:00,587
safeguarding the lives and property of the people in Yanbei,

453
00:42:00,587 --> 00:42:04,873
and contributing actively to the fire safety in our jurisdiction.

454
00:42:04,873 --> 00:42:06,924
Today,

455
00:42:06,924 --> 00:42:10,030
